      "raw_text": "A consignment of about $4,000\nworth of windmills and irrigation\npumps have been received by the\nWashington Land & Irrigation Co,\nof this city This is said to be the\nfirst shipment of an extensive pur-\nchase of such machinery. which\nwill be utilized in the improve\nment of Fairview heights, COM\nprising 1000 acres of irrigated land\n61b miles from Spokane."
